0065|- [HelpText]
0066|#COLOR_CHANGE=<expression>,<max>
S   |              <          > <   >
0067|*(in GPLOT and PLOT operations for families of curves)
0068|*selects the line color for each curve individually according to the
0069|*<expression> depending on any of the cycling parameters. The color
S   | <          >
0070|*indices are selected modulo <max>. Then the possible values are
S   |                             <   >
0071|*0,1,2,...,<max>-1 .
S   |           <   >
0073|*Each color may be selected separately by COLOR(n) specifications.
0075|*For example,
0076|*GPLOT Y(X)=A
0077|*YSCALE=0(1)15 X=[line_width(15)],-10,10,20
0078|*COLOR_CHANGE=A   A=0,15,1
0079|*displays the entire 16 color palette as horizontal bars.
