0125|+TITLE? þ PRINT CUR+1,E TO q113_07.html
0126|- include HTML40.DEV
0127|- include Q.DV2
0128|- [HelpText]
0129|*By default each Survo graphics window has a title bar above the
0130|*graph. The title bar text has the form
0131|*C3: SURVO MM Graphics
0132|*Where C identifies the current Survo session (blank=A,B,C,D,...)
0133|*and 3 # of the current graphics window in that session.
0135|*The text can be replaced by any other giving the specification
0136|*TITLE=<text>.
S   |       <    >
0138|*The title bar is completely omitted if specification WSTYLE=0 is used.
0140|- shadow a: [LINK(q113_01.html)]
0141|*  S = More information on GPLOT specifications
S   |   a                                          |
0142|E
0144|+WSTYLE? þ PRINT CUR+1,E TO q113_08.html
0145|- include HTML40.DEV
0146|- include Q.DV2
0147|- [HelpText]
0148|*In a Survo graphics window the title bar is left out by giving
0149|*the specification WSTYLE=0 in the GPLOT scheme.
0150|*Such a window cannot be moved or resized by the mouse. It can,
0151|*however, be closed by clicking it and pressing alt-F4.
0152|*Also the GPLOT /DEL <ALL or #> command closes such windows.
S   |                     <        >
0154|- shadow a: [LINK(q113_01.html)]
