0159|- include HTML40.DEV
0160|- include Q.DV2
0161|- [HelpText]
0162|*The logical coordinates (determined usually by the MODE specification)
0163|*of a point clicked by the mouse in a Survo graphics window can be saved
0164|*as a text file by giving a specification
0165|*MOUSE=<pathname_of_file>
S   |       <                >
0166|*in the GPLOT scheme.
0167|*The information is saved in the text file as a single line of the form
0168|*<# of window> <L or R> <x coordinate> <y coordinate>.
S   | <           > <      > <            > <            >
0169|*The button pressed is indicated by L (left) or R (right).
0171|*The MOUSE specification is intended for sucros working with graphics
0172|*windows and enables mouse-controlled activities with Survo graphics.
0174|- shadow a: [LINK(q113_01.html)]
